== 無線數據通訊紀錄 ==
在2012年5月，日本[[東京工業大學|東京工業大學]]的研究團隊使用T-射線的無線數據傳輸創下新的紀錄，發表在''{{tsl|en|Electronics Letters|}}''<ref>{{cite journal |title=Direct intensity modulation and wireless data transmission characteristics of terahertz-oscillating resonant tunneling diodes |author=K. Ishigaki, M. Shiraishi, S. Suzuki, M. Asada, N. Nishiyama, and S. Arai |date=10 May 2012 |volume=48 |issue=10 |pages=582–3 |doi=10.1049/el.2012.0849 |journal=Electronics Letters}}</ref>，並建議在未來以此做為數據傳輸的頻率。該團隊的[[概念驗證|概念驗證]]裝置使用[[谐振隧穿二极管|諧振穿隧二極體（RTD）]]，其電壓下降時的電流增加造成二極體“共振”，並產生THz波段的波。使用該RTD，研究人員發送出542 GHz的訊號，得到的數據傳輸速率是每秒3 Gigabits。該展示速度比當時主流的Wi-Fi [[802.11n|802.11n]]標準快20倍，比之前11月份的數據傳輸設置的紀錄快一倍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.techradar.com/news/internet/scientists-show-off-the-future-of-wi-fi-smash-through-3gbps-barrier-1080568 |title=Scientists show off the future of Wi-Fi – smash through 3Gbps barrier |first=Marc |last=Chacksfield |date=16 May 2012 |work=Tech Radar |accessdate=16 May 2012 |archive-date=2012-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121125063410/http://www.techradar.com/news/internet/scientists-show-off-the-future-of-wi-fi-smash-through-3gbps-barrier-1080568 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。THz Wi-Fi可能僅能在大約10米（33英尺）範圍內工作，但「理論上」數據傳輸速度可以高達100 Gbit/s。<ref name=BBC>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-18072618 |title=Milestone for Wi-Fi with 'T-rays' |date=16 May 2012 |work=BBC News |accessdate=16 May 2012 |archive-date=2012-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017120837/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-18072618 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

